[SN]TITLE[SN]
Olivier Awards 2017: Winners in full

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Harry Potter and the Cursed Child has won a record-breaking nine prizes at the Olivier Awards.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Here is the full list of winners (in bold) and the nominees for this year's awards, which took place at the Royal Albert Hall on Sunday 9 April.
